    "text": "This is a sentence displayed in the billing summary when a user makes a partial payment for additional storage. It informs the user that they are paying for a prorated amount of storage until their next billing date. `{{storageUnit}}` will be a unit of storage (e.g., \"Gigabyte\"), `{{startDate}}` is the current date, and `{{endDate}}` is the billing date.",
